316
00:23:55,120 --> 00:23:56,440
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

317
00:23:56,440 --> 00:23:57,330
On that New Year's Day,

318
00:23:57,330 --> 00:23:57,550
♪ Carefully drawing close to you ♪

319
00:23:57,550 --> 00:23:58,440
